import Book from "../Images/Book.gif"; function Stay() { const [show, setShow] = useState(false); const handleClose = () => setShow(false); const handleShow = () => setShow(true); const [efirstname, setfirstname] = useState(""); const [elastname, setlastname] = useState(""); const [eaddress, setaddress] = useState(""); const [ecity, setcity] = useState(""); const [estate, setstate] = useState(""); const [epincode, setpincode] = useState(""); const [ephonenumber, setphonenumber] = useState(""); const [eemail, setemail] = useState(""); const [echeck_in, setcheck_in] = useState(""); const [echeck_out, setcheck_out] = useState(""); const [msg, setMessage] = useState("") const onChangefirstname = (e) => setfirstname(e.target.value); const onChangelastname = (e) => setlastname(e.target.value); const onChangeaddress = (e) => setaddress(e.target.value); const onChangecity = (e) => setcity(e.target.value); const onChangestate = (e) => setstate(e.target.value); const onChangepincode = (e) => setpincode(e.target.value); const onChangephonenumber = (e) => setphonenumber(e.target.value); const onChangeemail = (e) => setemail(e.target.value); const onChangecheck_in = (e) => setcheck_in(e.target.value); const onChangecheck_out = (e) => setcheck_out(e.target.value); const handleSubmit = (evt) => { evt.preventDefault(); console.log(`HOTEL BOOKED:`); console.log(`FIRSTNAME: ${efirstname}`); console.log(`EMAIL: ${eemail}`); const userinfo = { firstname: efirstname, lastname: elastname, address: eaddress, city: ecity, state: estate, pincode:epincode, phonenumber: ephonenumber, email: eemail, }; axios.post("http://localhost:5000/admin/hotelbooking", userinfo).then((res) => { console.log(res.data); setMessage("HOTEL BOOKED"); }); setfirstname(""); setlastname(""); setaddress(""); setcity(""); setstate(""); setpincode(""); setphonenumber(""); setemail(""); setcheck_in(""); setcheck_out(""); }; return ( ); } export default Stay;
